race.description: In Memory Of Rita & Ron Englebrecht Mdn Hcp
race.comment: TWOEXCEL (11) overcame an awkward start to race on the speed only to tire late and miss the placings on debut last start over 1000m at Gunnedah. The blinkers going on should keep her mind on the job. Back in trip is a plus so she looks well placed to set the record straight. TORENDOSETTA (5) had a 44-day let-up before a modest effort last time out at Orange in soft going. Placed at his only run on a good track which was on debut back in January. Expecting a lot more today. STRAIGHT SOUTH (3) has been freshened up since a poor effort at Tamworth six weeks ago. Has trialled since and should be far more competitive. CAPSITY (8) last appeared when runner-up on debut over 1000m at Tamworth in July. Draws the fence and looks ready to run on the back of two recent trials. WON'THEARMECOMING (12) debuts for Angela Davies. Showed enough at her only trial to suggest she can compete here.
